    "\n",
    "## 🔹 4. Feature Extraction\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal:** Convert text → numerical vectors\n",
    "\n",
    "### Methods:\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Bag of Words (BoW)** → frequency-based\n",
    "* **TF-IDF** → importance-based\n",
    "* **Word Embeddings**:\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Word2Vec\n",
    "  * GloVe\n",
    "\n",
    "👉 Embeddings capture **semantic meaning** (very important concept)\n"
